  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Rehabilitation for 7 Burned Children in Peru</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will improve the life quality of 7 burned children in Peru through their integral rehabilitation, including medical treatment, physiotherapy, occupational therapy, psychological support, compression garments and the reintegration into the community. This way the kids get the opportunity to live a normal life after their traumatic burn accidents. Regrettably, these accidents are relatively common in Peru due to a lack of education and prevention.</narrative>
  </description>
